01:15.659 --> 01:20.538
Once, when I was six years old,
I read a book about the primeval forest.

01:23.375 --> 01:24.709
The book said,

01:24.835 --> 01:28.463
"Boa constrictors swallow
their prey whole, without chewing it."

01:32.843 --> 01:37.680
I pondered this deeply.
And then, I made my first drawing.

01:38.849 --> 01:41.225
I showed my masterpiece to grown-ups

01:41.351 --> 01:43.770
and asked if the drawing
frightened them.

01:43.854 --> 01:44.937
Frightened?

01:45.022 --> 01:47.815
Why should anyone
be frightened of a hat?

01:47.900 --> 01:49.484
Grown-ups.

01:49.651 --> 01:51.986
I never understand
anything by themselves.

01:52.696 --> 01:55.490
So, I made another drawing.

01:56.575 --> 01:59.285
Yes. My advice
is stick to arithmetic.

01:59.369 --> 02:01.662
- History.
- And grammar.

02:02.331 --> 02:06.000
I took their advice and I grew up.

02:07.711 --> 02:10.213
I forgot all about being a child.

02:11.173 --> 02:14.383
Until something miraculous happened.

02:28.398 --> 02:31.567
"The Little Prince"

02:38.742 --> 02:42.328
I've always wanted to find
someone to share my story with, but...

02:42.412 --> 02:44.330
I don't know, I...

02:44.414 --> 02:47.750
I guess this world just got too grown-up.

02:50.754 --> 02:55.758
Good morning, We manage the consequence
today figures we managed counter...

02:55.884 --> 02:58.636
Record-breaking numbers
were written down on pieces of paper,

02:58.762 --> 03:01.889
taken to the bank,
placed in drawers and locked with keys.

03:03.934 --> 03:05.768
Back straight.

03:06.270 --> 03:07.895
Listening attentively.

03:08.397 --> 03:09.438
Listening.

03:10.607 --> 03:12.441
No excessive blinking.

03:13.068 --> 03:14.694
Listening.

03:14.778 --> 03:17.154
Unexpected praise.

03:17.281 --> 03:20.408
Acknowledge and thank you.

03:21.159 --> 03:24.078
It's a smile, sweetie.
Show your teeth.

03:24.288 --> 03:26.455
No, Ooh. Not too much.

03:26.999 --> 03:28.416
Good. Okay.

03:28.959 --> 03:30.293
Now remember,

03:30.419 --> 03:33.754
accept holding an historical data tell
and leaning toward acceptance,

03:33.839 --> 03:35.882
they will ask only one question.

03:35.966 --> 03:37.008
