03:38.176 --> 03:40.511
"Are you Werth Academy material?"

03:41.805 --> 03:43.472
"Yes, I am."

03:44.141 --> 03:46.601
"Three things make me
Werth Academic Material...

03:53.984 --> 03:55.443
