03:57.321 --> 03:58.362
Go on.

04:19.301 --> 04:22.637
We've reviewed
your application, Good.

04:23.138 --> 04:24.513
Thank you!

04:25.933 --> 04:27.516
We've reviewed your transcripts...

04:27.643 --> 04:29.769
Thank... You.

04:34.816 --> 04:36.025
We've read your essay,

04:36.109 --> 04:39.028
"The transformative power of zero
on the bottom line"

04:39.154 --> 04:41.614
and the follow-up, "Zero, still my hero."

04:45.535 --> 04:48.204
Yes, you've done your work.
Everything looks to be in place.

04:51.124 --> 04:53.459
