- Stop!

05:19.236 --> 05:21.529
My unwavering...

05:21.905 --> 05:23.489
Abort... Abort.

05:23.657 --> 05:26.158
...con... concern, with.

05:27.244 --> 05:28.411
the...

05:32.165 --> 05:33.249
Thank you.

05:34.918 --> 05:36.085
Sweetie!

05:37.587 --> 05:41.757
"What do you want to be
when you grow up?"

05:41.842 --> 05:43.217
"Essential."

05:48.932 --> 05:51.892
Apparently,
they changed the big question.

05:54.271 --> 05:55.896
I'm sorry, Mom.

05:56.565 --> 05:57.898
Don't be.

05:58.400 --> 06:00.026
We'll just gonna have to go to Plan B.

06:00.110 --> 06:01.193
"B"?

06:01.278 --> 06:03.195
You said Plan B was impossible!

06:03.280 --> 06:04.520
That's why we went with Plan A.

06:05.115 --> 06:07.116
Plan B is the new Plan A.

06:08.535 --> 06:10.286
We're moving forward!

06:12.080 --> 06:13.539
Neighbourhood identified. Check.

06:13.623 --> 06:17.043
If by some miracle we can find
a house in the neighborhood we can afford. 

06:17.127 --> 06:18.999
they will have to take you.

